11.  Read, use, comment, and send me E-mail!!!

	Hope this is to your liking.  If you distribute these files,
put them on an ftp site, or whatever, please distribute all three files
that you received together.  Something like:  HTML_Ref.1.tar.Z.  If you do
put this doc on an ftp site, please be kind and post the updated
versions when you get them and remove the outdated versions.

